quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,97,"“Tukunnumbila Allah! Chisimu uwwe twaliji nkusokonechela kwakuonechela.”"
  26,98,"“Pandema jatwannandanyaga ŵanganyammwe ni M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,99,"“Ni nganatusokonesya ikaŵeje akuleŵa.”"
  27,70,"Ni ngasimwadandaulila ŵanganyao, soni ngasim’ba pakangani ligongo lya malindi gaakutenda."
  27,71,"Ŵanganyao ni akutiji: “Ana chele chilangachi chiyiche chakachi nam’baga jenumanja nkuŵecheta yakuona?”"
  27,72,"Jilani: “Kuŵankuŵa ili dusi munyuma mwenumo ine mwa ayila yankuŵa nkuikulumisya”"
  28,43,"Soni chisimu pamasile patwampele Musa Chitabu panyuma pakujijonanga mikutula jandanda, kuŵa muli kwa ŵandu, chongolo nambo soni chanasa kuti ŵanganyao akumbuchile."
  28,44,"Ni nganim’ba mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) kuupande wa kwigulo (kwetumbi) pandema jatwampaga Musa lilamusi (lya utume), nambo soni nganim’ba mwa akutendela umboni."
  28,45,"Nambo Uwwe twagumbile mikutula (jejinji panyuma pa Musa), ni galewipe maumi gao (mwanti mpaka syaliŵaliche abali sya achimitume). Soni mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) nganintameje ku ŵandu ŵa ku Madiyana ni kwasoomelaga ma Ȃya Getu, (kwanti mpaka ni nsimanye abali syao), nambo Uwwe ni ŵatuŵele Akutumisya (achimitume ni kutumisya abali syao kukwenu)."
  29,10,"Soni chilikati cha ŵandu pana ŵakutiji: “Tukulupilile mwa Allah.” Nambo naga ali apedwile masausyo ligongo lya Allah, akasagatenda masausyo ga ŵandu nti chisawu ilagasyo ya Allah, sano naga chili chiyiche chikulupusyo chakuumila kwa Ambuje ŵenu chisimu (achinakunaku) akutiji: “Chisimu uwwe twaliji namwe imo,” (nambo chitamilecho ali nkulambusya). Ana nganaŵa Allah kuti ni Jwakumanyilila nnope yaili m’mitima mwa iwumbe yosope?"
  29,11,"Sano Allah tiŵamanyukule kusyene aŵala ŵakulupilile ni tiŵamanyukule soni kusyene achinakunaku."
  29,12,"Sano aŵala ŵakanile ni akutiji pakwasalila aŵala ŵakulupilile: “Kuyani litala lyetu; ni chitukantwichilile ileŵi yenu.” Kutendaga ŵanganyao nganaŵa ajile kwatwichilila mu ileŵi yao chilichose. Chisimu ŵanganyao ŵaunami."